'''以色列议会议长'''({{lang-he-n|יוֹשֵׁב רֹאשׁ הכנסת}}, ''Yoshev Rosh HaKnesset'') ，是[[以色列国会|以色列国会]]的議長。此外，当[[以色列总统|以色列总统]]未能履行職務時，议长则代行总统职权。现任议长{{link-en|亞里夫·萊文|Yariv Levin}}，於2020年5月17日上任，为[[利庫德集團|利庫德集團]]成员。
<!--To date, {{link-en|Ahdut HaAvoda}}'s {{link-en|Nahum Nir}} and [[藍與白|藍與白]]'s [[本尼·甘茨|本尼·甘茨]] are the only Speakers not to have come from the ruling party, though in two cases ({{link-en|Avraham Burg}} and [[鲁文·里夫林|鲁文·里夫林]]) the party of the speaker ({{link-en|One Israel}} and [[利库德集团|利库德集团]] respectively) lost power during their term.

The speaker is expected to act in a non-partisan nature, but may occasionally take part in debates, and is allowed to vote.

The speaker is assisted by a number of ''Deputy Speakers of the Knesset'' (currently 10). The Deputy Speakers are drawn from the breadth of parties represented in the Knesset. Together, the Speaker and the Deputy Speakers constitute the Praesidium of the Knesset.-->

